<h2 class="item1">Introduction</h2>
<p>This module allows you to display social icons that are set on the product page. In this way, it gives your site visitors an opportunity to share links to the products of your store in different social networks</p>
<figure class="img-polaroid"><img src="img/magento/sharing-1.jpg" alt="" /></figure>
<p>This solution is implemented with the help of the popular Addthis service. This service allows you to set up the display of social icons and to integrate additional instruments for tracking your website usersâ€™ activity.</p>